item.title: Installer
item.description: SPECIFICATIONS - INSTALLER [TO BE COMPLETED] System compatibility [TO BE COMPLETED] A warning notification should be displayed to let the users know about a possible limitation if the server configuration is too low, cf. to do #9561 issue: Limitation of the server configuration: the set_time_limit function must be enabled on your web server for PrestaShop to run correctly. in Install.
